<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BookThing Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    integrity="sha384-r4NyP46KrjDleawBgD5tp8Y7UzmLA05oM1iAEQ17CSuDqnUK2+k9luXQOfXJCJ4I" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vesper+Libre&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">   
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/home.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header id="showcase" class="d-flex text-center text-white bg-dark">

    <div class="content-wrap d-flex w-100 h-100 p-3 mx-auto flex-column">
        <a href="/books"><button class="btn btn-browse">BROWSE</button></a>

        <h1><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="1em" height=".65em" fill="#4d2814" class="bi bi-book-half" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M8.5 2.687c.654-.689 1.782-.886 3.112-.752 1.234.124 2.503.523 3.388.893v9.923c-.918-.35-2.107-.692-3.287-.81-1.094-.111-2.278-.039-3.213.492V2.687zM8 1.783C7.015.936 5.587.81 4.287.94c-1.514.153-3.042.672-3.994 1.105A.5.5 0 0 0 0 2.5v11a.5.5 0 0 0 .707.455c.882-.4 2.303-.881 3.68-1.02 1.409-.142 2.59.087 3.223.877a.5.5 0 0 0 .78 0c.633-.79 1.814-1.019 3.222-.877 1.378.139 2.8.62 3.681 1.02A.5.5 0 0 0 16 13.5v-11a.5.5 0 0 0-.293-.455c-.952-.433-2.48-.952-3.994-1.105C10.413.809 8.985.936 8 1.783z"/>
          </svg>BookThing</h1>
        <p><b>READ THE NEXT BEST THING!</b></p>
        <div class="user-buttons">
          <%if(!currentUser){%>
            <a href="/login"><button class="btn btn-left">sign in</button></a>
            <a href="/register"><button class="btn btn-right">sign up</button></a>
          <%}else{%>
            <a href="/users/<%=currentUser._id%>"><button class="btn">My Account</button></a>
          <%}%>
            
        </div>
        
</div>
</header>

<section id="bookDisplay">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-3 p-3">Discover Only The Best</h2>
    <div class="row gx-3 gy-1 mb-3">
      <%for(let book of books){%>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3 py-5">
          <div class="card shadow h-100 mx-auto" style="width: 12rem;">
            <a href="/books/<%=book._id%>"><img src="<%=book.image%>" class="img-thumbnail" alt=""></a>
            <div class="card-body book-cards">
              <a href="/books/<%=book._id%>"><h5 class="card-title"><%=book.title%></h5></a>
                <h6 class="card-subtitle"><%=book.author%></h6>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%}%>
  
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="bookReview" class="p-3">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center py-3 mb-4">Express Your Bookish Emotions</h2>
    <div class="reviews">
      <div class="row mb-4 g-2">
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center">
          <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1345958969l/128029.jpg" class="img-thumbnail" style="width: 12rem" alt="book review 1">
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 align-self-center justify-content-md-center">
          <div class="content-width">
            <blockquote class="mb-4 blockquote">"I te wahangūtanga o te iwi, ka tīkina atu e Māui te kauae a tōna tipuna mai i tana tātau, me tana piupiu haere. He maha ngā mea i kīia kāore e taea, ēngari i taea e au, 
              te tiki i te ahi mai i a Mahuika, te heke atu ki Rarohenga."</blockquote>
              <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">
              <b>Sheldon Cooper</b>
              </figcaption>
          </div>
         
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
 

  <div class="reviews">
    <div class="row mb-4 g-2">
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center order-sm-1">
        <img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386605169l/17899948.jpg" class="img-thumbnail" style="width: 12rem" alt="book review 1">
       
        </div>
        
      <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 align-self-center justify-content-md-center mb-4">
        <div class="content-width">
          <blockquote class="mb-4 blockquote">"Ā, tere tonu tētahi o ngā tuākana ahi.  hopu i te rā, he nui ake i ngā manu kua mau i a koe! Ka rongo koe i tōna wera, ka kī atu tētahi. 
            "Te āhua nei kua pakapaka ōna whakaaro i te rā, te kī a tētahi atu, me tā rātau kata anō."</blockquote>
            <figcaption class="blockquote-footer">
              <b>Will Wheaton</b>
              </figcaption>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    <section id="bookShelf">
      <div class="container p-4 text-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-4">Record Your Reading Obsession</h2>
          <h4>Ellie has read <span style="color:red"><b>25</b></span> books!</h4>
          <h4>Sam has read <span style="color:red"><b>38</b></span> books!</h4>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <div class="footer-width">
        <h5 class="text-center p-5">&copy; 2022, BookThing</h5>
      </div>
        
   </footer>
 
   <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
       integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo"
       crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
   <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/5.0.0-alpha1/js/bootstrap.min.js"
       integrity="sha384-oesi62hOLfzrys4LxRF63OJCXdXDipiYWBnvTl9Y9/TRlw5xlKIEHpNyvvDShgf/"
       crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>
</html>